            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Yes?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Excuse me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Cory! Do you need something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "...I brought the items you requested."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Ah, the \"Spirit Needles\"!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "One, two, three... Yeah, there's enough here! Thank you so much!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...Huh? Cory, did you get a little shorter, by any chance?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I rushed a little too much for you... I'm a little tired now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "But I'm okay. I'm sure I'll be back to normal soon enough. I drank the milk you brought me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Cory..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, seeing how I delivered the items, I'll be leaving now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Okay, thank you again, Cory! I'll go visit your shop again soon!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I'll be waiting..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "These \"Spirit Needles\" Cory made... With this many, I should be able to make a device to move Plachta's soul."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Yeah... I'll do it!"
        }
    ]
